Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:42.75,Tema_Ranka,,0000,0000,0000,,Noina miria enderu purodea
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.26,0:23:45.41,Tema_Ranka,,0000,0000,0000,,Fotomi
